'''Will Simpson''' (born [[June 9]], [[1959]]) is an [[United States|American]] [[show jumping]] competitor and Olympic champion.<ref>
{{cite web
 | url        = http://sports.yahoo.com/olympics/beijing/USA/Will+Simpson/221827
 | accessdate = 2008-08-18
 | title      = Will Simpson
 | work       = Beijing Olympics
 | publisher  = [[Yahoo! Sports]] }}</ref>

At the [[2008 Summer Olympics]] in [[Beijing]], Simpson won the [[gold medal]] as part of the United States team in [[Equestrian at the 2008 Summer Olympics - Team jumping|team jumping]], together with [[McLain Ward]], [[Laura Kraut]], and [[Beezie Madden]].<ref>
